{"name": "canada-holiday", "metadata": {"name": "canada-holiday", "version": "1.1.6", "classifiers": ["Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": "https://github.com/kmsunmin/canada-holiday", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "Python package for Canadian holidays", "upload_time": 1732988249}, "documentation": ["# canada-holiday\n\n![example workflow](https://github.com/kmsunmin/canada-holiday/actions/workflows/run-tests.yml/badge.svg)\n\na Python package for retrieving Canadian holidays information for all provinces for any given year.\n\n## Installation\n\n### With pip:\n```bash\npip install canada-holiday\n```\n\n### With poetry:\n```bash\npoetry add canada-holiday\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```python\nimport datetime\nimport canada_holiday\n\non_holidays_2023 = canada_holiday.get_holidays(\"Ontario\", 2023)\n# prints \"Getting holiday information of Ontario province...\"\nprint(on_holidays_2023)\n# [CanadaHoliday(New Year's Day, 2023-01-01, Sunday, all), CanadaHoliday(Family Day, 2023-02-20, Monday, Ontario), ...]\n\nmanitoba_holidays_2023_june = canada_holiday.get_holidays(\"MB\", 2023, 2)\n# prints \"Getting holiday information of Manitoba province...\"\nprint(manitoba_holidays_2023_june)\n# [CanadaHoliday(Louis Riel Day, 2023-02-20, Monday, Manitoba)]\nlouis_riel_day = manitoba_holidays_2023_june[0]\nprint(louis_riel_day.name)\n# Louis Riel Day\nprint(louis_riel_day.month)\n# 2\nprint(louis_riel_day.day)\n# 20\nprint(louis_riel_day.date)\n# 2023-02-20\nprint(louis_riel_day.province)\n# Manitoba\nprint(louis_riel_day.day_of_the_week)\n# Monday\n\ndate = datetime.date(2023, 8, 7)\nresult = canada_holiday.is_holiday(date, \"British Columbia\")\n# prints \"2023-08-07 is a holiday, B.C. Day in British Columbia province(s) in Canada\"\nprint(result)\n# True\ndate = datetime.date(2023, 4, 5)\nresult = canada_holiday.is_holiday(date, \"Nova Scotia\")\n# prints \"2023-04-05 is not a holiday in Nova Scotia province.\"\nprint(result)\n# False\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info.national", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info.national.HOLIDAYS", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info.on", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info.on.ONTARIO", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info.nb", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info.nb.NEW_BRUNSWICK", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info.sk", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info.sk.SASKATCHEWAN", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info.bc", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info.bc.BRITISH_COLUMBIA", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info.ns", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info.ns.NOVA_SCOTIA", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info.yt", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "canada_holiday.holiday_info.yt.YUKON", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canada_holiday.utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "canada_holiday.utils.check_province_name", "asynchronous": f